	dprr:hasNoteText "A Tribune against whom Cato directed an important speech (FOR 1.47-50, 182-184), dated conjecturally in Cato's consulship by Münzer (RE), and in his censorship by Malcovati (FOR) and Niccolini (FTP 117f.)." .
